quran[59]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,“Hâ-Mîm
  44,2,“Ndikulumbilira buku lofotokoza momveka
  44,3,“Ndithu tidaivumbulutsa (Qur’an) mu usiku wodala. Ife ndithu Ndiachenjezi
  44,4,“Mu (usiku) umenewu chinthu chilichonse chanzeru chimaweruzidwa ndi kulongosoledwa
  44,5,“Mwa chilamulo chochokera kwa Ife. Ndithu Ife ndife otumiza atumiki (kuti achenjeze anthu)
  44,6,"“(Chifukwa cha) chifundo chochokera kwa Mbuye wako. Ndithu Iye Ngwakumva zonse, Wodziwa kwabasi"
  44,7,"“Mbuye wa thambo ndi nthaka ndi zapakati pake, ngati muli otsimikiza"
  44,8,"“Palibe wopembedzedwa moona koma Iye basi. Amapereka moyo ndikupereka imfa, Mbuye wanu ndi Mbuye wa makolo anu oyamba"
  44,9,"“Koma iwo (okanira) ali mchikaiko akungosewera, (potsatira zilakolako zawo zoipa)"
  44,10,"“Basi, yembekezera tsiku limene thambo lidzadze ndi utsi woonekera (konsekonse)"
  44,11,"“Udzawaphimba anthu onse (ndipo adzakhala akunena:) “Ichi ndi chilango chowawa"
  44,12,"“E Mbuye wathu! Tichotsereni chilangochi, ndithu ife tikhulupirira.”"
  44,13,“(Kodi lero) kukumbukira kuwapindulira chiyani iwo? Chikhalirecho mtumiki wolongosola chilichonse adawadzera
  44,14,"“Koma sadamlabadire uku akumnena kuti: “Waphunzitsidwa (ndi anthu), ndiponso wopenga.”"
  44,15,“Ndithu Ife tichotsa chilangocho pang’ono (koma) inu mubwerezanso (machimo anu)
  44,16,"“(Kumbuka, iwe Mtumiki), tsiku limene tidzawalanga chilango chachikulu; ndithu Ife ndife olanga"
  44,17,"“Ndipo ndithu iwo asadadze, tidawayesa anthu a Farawo. Ndiponso adawadzera mtumiki wolemekezeka"
  44,18,"“Kuti: “Ndipatseni akapolo a Allah. Ndithu ine kwa inu ndi Mtumiki wokhulupirika.”"
  44,19,““Ndipo musadzikweze kwa Allah. Ndithu ine ndikubweretserani chisonyezo choonekera.”
  44,20,““Ndipo Ine ndadzitchinjiriza ndi Mbuye Wanga ndiponso Mbuye wanu (ku chiwembu chofuna kundipha) pondigenda (ndi miyala).”
  44,21,"““Ndipo ngati simundikhulupirira, ndipatukeni (musandivutitse).”"
  44,22,"““(Koma adamchitira mtopola). Ndipo iye adaitana Mbuye wake kuti: “Awa ndithu ndi anthu oipa.”"
  44,23,"“(Allah adamuuza kuti): “Pita ndi akapolo Anga usiku; ndithu inu mulondoledwa.”"
  44,24,"““Ndipo isiye nyanja ili momwemo, zii. ndithu iwo ndikhamu (lankhondo) limene limizidwa.”"
  44,25,“Kodi ndi minda ingati ndi akasupe zomwe adazisiya atamizidwa
  44,26,“Ndiponso mmera ndi malo abwino
  44,27,“Ndi mtendere (waukulu) umene adali kusangalala nawo mmenemo
  44,28,“Umo ndi mmene zidalili. Ndipo tidawapatsa anthu ena zimenezo
  44,29,“Thambo ndi nthaka sizidawalilire ndipo sadapatsidwe mpata (wobwereranso pa dziko)
  44,30,“Ndipo ndithu tidapulumutsa ana a Israyeli ku chilango choyalutsa
  44,31,“Chochokera kwa Farawo; ndithu iye adali wodzikweza ndiponso mmodzi wa opyola malire
  44,32,“Ndipo ndithu tidawasankha (Ayuda nthawi imeneyo) pa mitundu ina m’kudziwa Kwathu
  44,33,“Ndipo tidawapatsa zisonyezo (kupyolera m’dzanja la Mûsa) momwe mudali mayeso oonekera poyera kwa iwo
  44,34,“Ndithu awa (Aquraish) akunena (kuti)
  44,35,"““Palibe china choposera pa imfa yathu yoyambayi, ndipo ife sitidzaukitsidwa.”"
  44,36,"““Choncho tibweretsereni makolo athu (amene adafa), ngati mukunena zoona (kuti kuli kuuka).”"
  44,37,"“Kodi iwo ndi abwino (ndi kupambana pa nyonga), kapena anthu a Tubba (mafumu a kudziko la Yemen) ndi amene adalipo kale iwo asadadze? Tidawaononga. Ndithu iwo adali oipa"
  44,38,"“Ndipo sitidalenge thambo ndi nthaka ndi zimene zili pakati paizo, mwachibwana"
  44,39,“Sitidalenge ziwirizi koma mwachoonadi; koma anthu ambiri sakudziwa
  44,40,“Ndithu tsiku lachiweruziro ndiyo nthawi yawo onse (imene alonjezedwa)
  44,41,"“Tsiku limene m’bale sadzathandiza m’bale wake pa chilichonse (ku chilango cha Allah), ngakhale iwo sadzapulumutsidwa"
  44,42,"“Kupatula amene Allah adzawachitira chifundo. Ndithu Iye Ngwamphamvu zoposa, Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  44,43,“Ndithu mtengo wa Zakkumi
  44,44,“Ndi chakudya cha ochimwa
  44,45,"“(Kutentha kwake) ngati mtovu wosungunulidwa, (wotentha kwambiri;) udzakhala ukuwira mmimba"
  44,46,“Monga kuwira kwa madzi otentha kwambiri
  44,47,"“(Kudzanenedwa): “Mgwireni; mkokereni (ndi kumponya) pakatikati pa Jahena!”"
  44,48,““Kenako mthireni pamwamba pamutu wake chilango chamadzi otentha!”
  44,49,"“(Adzauzidwa mwachipongwe): “Lawa! Ndithu iwe ndiwe wamphamvu zambiri, wolemekezeka, (monga momwe udali kudzitamira muja).”"
  44,50,““Ndithu izi ndi zimene mudali kuzikaikira zija!”
  44,51,“Ndithu oopa Allah adzakhala pa malo a chitetezo
  44,52,“Mminda ndi mu akasupe
  44,53,“Adzavala (nsalu) za silika wopyapyala ndi silika wokhuthala uku atayang’anizana (nkhope)
  44,54,“Umo ndi mmene zidzakhalire; ndipo tidzawakwatitsa ndi akazi okongola amaso aakulu
  44,55,"“Mmenemo adzakhala akuitanitsa mtundu uliwonse wa zipatso, mwamtendere"
  44,56,"“Sadzalawa imfa mmenemo, kupatula imfa yoyamba ija; ndipo adzawateteza kuchilango cha Jahena"
  44,57,“Chifundo chochokera kwa Mbuye wako! Kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwakukulu
  44,58,“Ndithu taifewetsa (Qur’an) mchiyankhulo chako (cha Chiarabu) kuti akumbukire
  44,59,"“Choncho yembekeza; iwonso akuyembekezera, (kodi ndani chimtsikire chilango pakati panu)"